reviews.text: Good small hotel,  extremely  busy throughout the day.  Close proximity to mtr Prince Edward... Rooms r clean and well maintained.  Staff is friendly and helpful... We had a breakfast option included...breakfast got boring after day two as they had the same stuff on the menu... Overall a very good experience...

Love the hotel for its super strategic location..
Tons of good food surrounding...
Near MRT station - Prince Edward, 5 minutes walk
Near Ladies Market, Mongkok Flower Market

Improvement area is their bed....

The hotel has a very good location, just 3-min walk from the metro station and around 10-15 mins from Mongkok night market. The staff are very hospitable and accommodating. The amenities and facilities are complete. My family and I loved the buffet breakfast! I would highly recommend this hotel!

Strategic place, 3 minutes walk to MRT station, 8 minutes walk to shopping area and mal. Busses and taxi goes through. Affordable price. Everything is fine. But difficult to get toilet after you check out.

Great hotel. They have a mini cafe and buffet. Accessible with elevator. Cute items are for sale on the store such as wallets and suit case, The location is near almost the most convenience stores, local restaurants, money changers, and atm. It is safe to go outside at night also if want to go to the night market.

reviews.text: Good taste with reasonable price
Taste amazing. A lot of variation menu. From dim sum until chinese food and seafood. Everything you can get here. Suitable for family or special event

Staffs are not the best but the food is awesome. Everytime i go back to hongkong i will at least go there once a week. If u are not more than 2 you will probably need to share a table. And dont forget to bring napkins!!!

reviews.text:
位置很方便，出品碟頭大，食味不錯，價錢合理，適合大夥兒聚會。
但環境比較嘈！
食物有水準，可惜獨立房有無品食客吸煙，二手煙氣味影響大堂其他食客。
於特價時食阿拉斯加長腳蟹（５至６斤） 二千元可下樓

(維景酒店分店)
交通方便，地方光猛闊落
套餐款式多，抵食！
曾經到過這酒家兩次，整體印象好，食材新鮮，地方尚可接受。地点交通方便，四通八達，附近商店林立，應有盡有，朋友飯局不防一試。
